{"tid":2095349,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"錢禮疑因外籍不獲任國安法官","createTime":"2020-07-05T11:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T12:02:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a52ece0cdc2a381a8abd038d1fdd4d8a73c8e3b5","tid":2095349,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:24:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200705/IMGLYRSKP472VMMPQW7T44D5YA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200705%2FIMGLYRSKP472VMMPQW7T44D5YA%2F&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj37VsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=0c31163c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200705%2FIMGLYRSKP472VMMPQW7T44D5YA%2F&h=b38e19d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200705/IMGLYRSKP472VMMPQW7T44D5YA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n錢禮疑因外籍不獲任國安法官<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥前日指派六名法官處理國安法案件，卻沒有公開法官名單，只得總裁判官蘇惠德承認獲得指派。《星島》昨引消息指，其他獲指定法官均為裁判法院主任裁判官，但東區法院主任裁判官錢禮卻因國籍問題不獲指派。有立法會議員憂慮，未來終審法院的外籍法官也會被拒諸門外。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：職員指覆檢大量書籍從未見 或歷時半年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jXqsEWaEj-Eaym70huN16bsUP2Q=/314x473/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ANAST4JRSK7RLTO643ZLPICMGE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjXqsEWaEj-Eaym70huN16bsUP2Q%3D%2F314x473%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FANAST4JRSK7RLTO643ZLPICMGE.gif&h=bebe0f91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n錢禮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋憂日後排除終院洋法官<br />\n<br />\n《星島》報道，除蘇惠德，其他獲林鄭指派處理國安法案件的裁判官包<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n查港版國安法，不見有條款規定外籍法官不可被指派。<br />\n<br />\n終審法院首席法官馬道立日前發聲明指，擁有外國籍的法官並不排除在指定（審理國安法案件）法官之外。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-KXzdykPdiPCXKtIsqOf8QVx4EU=/1013x659/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EUXV5FO6YSQ2TR65OY7IXGUBCE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-KXzdykPdiPCXKtIsqOf8QVx4EU%3D%2F1013x659%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEUXV5FO6YSQ2TR65OY7IXGUBCE.gif&h=27392658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前日政府表示，林鄭是在徵詢國安委和終審法院首席法官的意見後，再作出指定法官的決定。本報就指派事宜向司法機構查詢，機構着記者向特首辦查詢。特首辦則表示「不評論揣測」。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員、大律師楊岳橋批評，林鄭至今未有公開指派法官的客觀標準，「以往政府委任法官時，都會提供返履歷原因，今次有乜唔見得光？」有報道指有法官因其外籍身份不獲委任，他關注林鄭曾否否決馬道立推薦的人選，必須盡快交代，否則會令人擔心連終院的非常任外籍法官也可被排拒在外。<br />\n<br />\n這批裁判官在處理反送<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n判監案例。"},{"pid":"c9bfdfedc0bde776274c84701439c44a73144f46","tid":2095349,"uid":238370,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:33:30.000Z","msg":"唔比錢禮做係佢嘅福份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b45e648f839c8a693287dd3d423aacbc2f7f435","tid":2095349,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9bfdfedc0bde776274c84701439c44a73144f46","tid":2095349,"uid":238370,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:33:30.000Z","msg":"唔比錢禮做係佢嘅福份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:37:37.000Z","msg":"多謝港共🙏🏻"},{"pid":"1fc45a13b085b126393c89521201c2f57e2825a7","tid":2095349,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:40:15.000Z","msg":"睇相似選坐館多過選法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b2fa25066caa78cef4fad219e1b4f91641b557","tid":2095349,"uid":97398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fc45a13b085b126393c89521201c2f57e2825a7","tid":2095349,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:40:15.000Z","msg":"睇相似選坐館多過選法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:48:12.000Z","msg":"有中國特色的任命法官"},{"pid":"73d24